OL,7,FA driver who fled the scene after
OL,8,Fkilling a mother and her son in head-
OL,9,Fon car crash in Derbyshire has been
OL,10,Fjailed.
OL,12,FJoshua Hill was driving a BMW X3 on
OL,13,Fthe A632 Chesterfield Road at Span
OL,14,FCarr near Kelstedge on December 9th,
OL,15,F2023 when he attempted to overtake a
OL,16,Fcar in the driving rain.
OL,18,FThe 27-year-old collided head-on with
OL,19,Fa Hyundai i20 travelling in the
OL,20,Fopposite direction.
