OL,7,FAngela Boyack, the front seat
OL,8,Fpassenger of the Hyundai, died
OL,9,Finstantly.
OL,11,FHer son Stephen, who was driving the
OL,12,Fcar, suffered serious injuries and was
OL,13,Ftaken to hospital where he died a
OL,14,Fshort time later.
OL,16,FHill ran from the scene, stopping a
OL,17,Fpassing motorist and asking for a lift
OL,18,Finto Chesterfield, before getting the
OL,19,Fbus to Sheffield.
