OL,7,FHe then hid at various properties in
OL,8,Fthe city for two days before being
OL,9,Farrested on December 11th.
OL,11,FAngela's husband and elder son were
OL,12,Ftravelling in a vehicle behind
OL,13,FStephen's and witnessed the
OL,14,Fdevastating collision.
OL,16,FIn a victim impact statement William
OL,17,FBoyack, Angela's husband and Stephen's
OL,18,Ffather, said: "I am still constantly
OL,19,Fhaving the most horrific and soul
OL,20,Fsickening flashbacks to the collision
OL,21,Fwhich continue to be crippling for me.
