OL,7,F"Why, why did you do this? That is
OL,8,Fwhat I want to know."
OL,10,FHill, from Sheffield, was charged with
OL,11,Fcausing death by dangerous driving,
OL,12,Fcausing death by driving while
OL,13,Funlicensed/uninsured, failing to stop
OL,14,Fafter an accident and failing to
OL,15,Freport an accident.
OL,17,FHe had denied the charges but entered
OL,18,Fa guilty plea on the first day of his
OL,19,Ftrial at Derby Crown Court on May 10th.
